name: WALLETS.TEZ x SUBDOMAINS
description: Every holder of this NFT will be entitled to their own subdomain of wallets.tez. I will update the owner of the subdomain to the wallet address that holds the NFT, at which point the NFT holder can log in to https://tezos.domains and change where the address points to. I guarantee this service to work until at least January of 2026. Contact @klickdotdev on Twitter for support.[www.klick.dev/links]
